DecisionTreeREADME.txt:
To use decision trees:

import decision_tree
dt = DecisionTree()
dt.fit(Xs, Ys)
dt.predict(example)

Where Xs, Ys, and example are all numpy arrays.

See more examples in sklearn_cv.py
For further help, contact michael.noseworthy@mail.mcgill.ca
